		<body>
				<p rend="align(center)">DEDICATION</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">OF THE</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Sephardim Synagogue&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">HOUSE OF <placeName>ISRAEL</placeName>&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><placeName>Baltimore</placeName>&#44; <date>September 16<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. 1857</date>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">PROGRAMME.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The bearers of the Law will form in the Vestry Room&#44; and walk in<lb/> Procession to the door of the Synagogue&#44; when the <persName>REV. SOLOMON JACOBS</persName>&#44;<lb/> of <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44; will knock at the door three times&#44; and say&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">&#8220;Open for me the gates of righteousness&#44; that I may enter through them&#44; to<lb/> praise the Lord.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The Minister inside answers&#58;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">&#8220;This is the gate of the Lord&#44; into which the righteous shall enter.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The persons bearing the Law enter and ascend the Tebah&#44; during which</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">THE CHOIR WILL SING A QUARTETTE&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">FROM <persName>MENDELSSHON&#39;S</persName> &#8220;ORATORIO OF <persName>ELIJAH</persName>.&#8221;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">After which the Congregation sing&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Baruch haba beshem adonai.</p>
				<p><persName>REV. J. M. D. SOLLA</persName>&#44; the Minister&#44; then says&#58;</p>
				<p>&#8220;Blessed art thou O Lord&#44; our God&#44; King of the Universe&#44; who hast preserved<lb/> us alive&#44; sustained us&#44; and brought us to enjoy this season&#33;&#8221;</p>
				<p>During which the PERPETUAL LAMP is lighted&#44;&#8212;and the</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">ARK OPENED.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">THE CHOIR SING ODECHA.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">THE SEVEN&#45;CIRCUITS.</p>
				<p>During which the Minister and Congregation alternately repeat the<lb/> following</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">PSALMS&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">30<hi rend="sup">th</hi>.    100<hi rend="sup">th</hi>.    122d.    127<hi rend="sup">th</hi>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Yimloch&#44; by Minister&#44; and 29<hi rend="sup">th</hi> Psalm by Congregation.</p>
				<p>After which the LAW is deposited in the ARK&#44;&#8212;the Minister says&#44;<lb/> &#8220;SHUBA&#44;&#8221;&#8212;when the doors of the Ark are closed.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">SERMON BY <persName>REV. ISAAC LEESER</persName>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">CONSECRATION HYMN&#44;</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">Composed expressly for the occasion by <persName>D. N. Carvalho&#44; Esq.</persName>&#44; sung by the CHOIR.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">SERMON BY <persName>REV. SOLOMON JACOBS</persName>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">SOLO.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">SYMPHONY&#44;</p>
				<p>During which free will Offerings will be collected.</p>
				<p>MISHEBERACHS will then be made for those who desire it.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">EVENING SERVICE BY <persName>REV. MR. LEESER</persName>.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)">YIGDAL BY CHOIR.</p>
				<p rend="align(center)"><persName>JOHN D. TOV</persName>&#44; PRINTER.</p>
			
